## Overview
This directory contains the official Standard Operating Procedure governing the execution of the month-end close.

The objective is to provide a **controlled, repeatable, and audit-defensible** process that delivers financial information which is:

- accurate  
- complete  
- timely  
- properly reviewed  

This SOP forms the foundation for all other finance control procedures.

---

## What This SOP Covers
The procedure defines mandatory standards for:

- Roles and responsibilities  
- Task lifecycle management  
- RAG risk visibility  
- Evidence and documentation  
- Treatment of estimates  
- Dependency management  
- Post-close adjustments  
- Version control  
- Governance and approval  

It applies to **all close activities**, **all entities**, and **all reporting periods**.

